-- Liu Supporter Pan Sentenced to Four Months in Donor Fraud
-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 2013-10-10T16:13:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-10/liu-supporter-pan-sentenced-to-four-months-in-donor-fraud.html
Xing Wu “Oliver” Pan, a supporter
of  New York  comptroller and mayoral candidate John Liu, was
sentenced to four months for a scheme to send thousands of
dollars in illegal contributions to his campaign using straw
donors.  Jia “Jenny” Hou, another Liu supporter, is scheduled to
be sentenced today in federal court in Manhattan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Hurtado in New York at 
 pathurtado@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mary Romano at 
 mromano6@bloomberg.net  